snippet.title: Official Mabinogi: Fantasy Life Trailer
snippet.description:
Be anyone you want to be, and live the fantasy life you’ve always dreamed of, in the world’s most expressive MMORPG adventure! 

Who will you be today? Play for FREE at http://mabinogi.nexon.net 

Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mabinogi 
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/MabiOfficial 
Follow us on Tumblr: http://mabiofficial.tumblr.com/
